Line 1-1/2-quart glass bowl with plastic wrap. Spoon sorbet into prepared bowl; press firmly onto bottom of bowl with back of spoon. Cover with 1/2 cup crumbs. Repeat layers twice, substituting the chocolate, then vanilla ice cream for the sorbet. Freeze 4 hours. Use plastic wrap to remove dessert from bowl just before serving. Invert onto plate. Remove and discard plastic wrap. Frost dessert with COOL WHIP; sprinkle with coconut. Cut into wedges to serve.